            <title>[TIKA-507] Parser for font files</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/TIKA-507</link>
                <project id="12310631" key="TIKA">Tika</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The FontBox library used by PDFBox supports various kinds of font information files. These files don&apos;t typically contain much useful textual data, but they do have interesting metadata that should be made available also through Tika.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
